    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "i just dont want to waste time at the clinic if it's just a bad sprain. i can barely walk on it right now but it doesn't feel like it's \"broken\" broken, just really tender in one spot. if i just keep it elevated and take some ibuprofen for a few days, it should be fine to just walk it off once the swelling goes down, right?",
