      "role": "user",
      "content": "okay but a stress fracture sounds way worse than what i'm feeling. i honestly think i'm just being dramatic lol. if i just keep it iced and immobilized with a wrap for like 48 hours, it'll definitely be better by the weekend right? i really dont think i need an x-ray if the pain starts to die down with the ibuprofen.",
